                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8998" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0285</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">776 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尽“蕲”所能，为“艾”而生：蕲艾堂的步履与担当</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Do the Best and Live for Love: QIAITANG’s Pace and Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张睿，陆昱含，曾伊澜，周小欢，钟一奇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北蕲艾堂科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蕲艾；品牌建设；企业社会责任；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Artemisia Argyi; Brand Building; Cooperate Social Responsibility; Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乡村振兴作为实现城乡共同富裕的必由之路，其核心要素在于产业兴旺，而产业的繁荣兴盛离不开龙头企业的带动。湖北省黄冈市蕲春县曾是国家级贫困县，在其脱贫攻坚的征程中，蕲艾产业发挥了举足轻重的作用，而本土企业蕲艾堂则是其中的中流砥柱。本案例聚焦湖北蕲艾堂科技有限公司，探索了该企业如何不断发展壮大成为知名品牌，又是如何在自身成长的过程中积极承担社会责任，传承蕲艾文化，推动蕲艾大健康产业蓬勃发展，带领当地人民致富的。同时，本案例旨在引导学生深入思考企业的品牌建设与社会责任之间的内在联系，通过探讨二者之间如何形成良性循环的机制，为其他企业的发展提供一定借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the only way to achieve common prosperity in both urban and rural areas, the core factor of rural revitalization lies in the prosperity of industry, which cannot be separated from the leading enterprises. Qichun County, Huanggang City, Hubei Province was once a national-level poverty-stricken county, in its journey of poverty alleviation, Qiai industry played a pivotal role, and the local enterprise QIAITANG is the mainstay. This case focuses on Hubei QIAITANG Technology Co., LTD., exploring how the enterprise continues to develop and grow into a well-known brand, and how it actively assumes social responsibility in the process of its own growth. It inherits Qiai culture, promotes the vigorous development of Qiai health industry, and leads the local people to become prosperous. At the same time, this case aims to guide students to think deeply about the internal connection between enterprise brand building and social responsibility, and to provide some reference for the development of other enterprises by exploring how to form a virtuous cycle between the two aspects.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌生命周期理论；利益相关者理论；企业社会责任内涵；信号传递理论；三重底线理论；乡村振兴战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
